The paper deals with semi-supervised learning in the context of image classification, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on deep learning methods for image classification, it is more likely to belong to the first three sub-categories mentioned above.
